Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates  who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after \NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were doing everything he says \Nin order to save your brother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your younger brother or older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try to save his life too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:52.72,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Noah Closing in! The Fish-Man \NIsland Facing Destruction!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Ship of Promise! "Noah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is doing it and how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit strange,  but \Nwhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a relic from history. \NIt serves no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't let anything \Nhappen to that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the proper day comes, no one \Nis allowed to move that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he took a lot of Energy \NSteroids and became a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What do you three want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume-sama, you are very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what Fish-Man Karate is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna work. Because \NI'm made of rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is nothing compared to Jimbei's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! That's why you \Nshouldn't depend on fake power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Shell Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Your head's gonna crack open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head was harder than iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get hit at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he know when they come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Observation Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama, he is unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's great! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how strong the \Nworld-renowned pirate is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I-Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Noah of the Fish-Man District?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Noah in the air over the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading towards this plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost broken through \Nthe bubble around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the bubble pops, the island is \Nfinished! We're all gonna get washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?!\N--The Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the ship hits, the whole \Nisland will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's operating it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it has an engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?!\N--It's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know what's happening \Nbut we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the sea will turn red \Nif we all get smashed at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Evacuate!\N--Get into the water off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! I slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Wadatsumi - working for Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vander Decken! I fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken?! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this one of your strategies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Decken is operating the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you good-for-nothings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How tough can he be?! I attacked \Nhim with the Armament Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Decken? That crazy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a part of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Decken threw the Noah \Nlike he threw those letters and axes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been loving you for 10 years \Nsince you were just a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one who could love you \Nlike I do in all the wide world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my love! Love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just accept it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that I throw with \Nmy Mark-Mark Fruit power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't stop until they crash into \Nsomething or hit their target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah the giant ship! It embodies \Nmy love for you! Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And drop dead along with all the \NFish-Man Island, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Decken! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wadatsumi! It's too late! It's \Nimpossible for me to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I need you to become a sacrifice upon \NShirahoshi's death, along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! The bubble is gonna pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did Princess Shirahoshi go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? She's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Princess! Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shirahoshi disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess Shirahoshi!\N--When did she go up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi! Why did she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that ship is flying towards her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to take just my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am the only one who you want to kill, \Nplease do not harm the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess-sama!\N--Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The Noah is changing its course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading towards \NPrincess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that crazy Decken bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was gonna crush us all \Nalong with the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he betray us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do something to save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How amazingly beautiful you are, \NShirahoshi! Even your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to take the \Nmatter into your own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to save the country, \Naren't you, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shira... hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eligible to become Vander \NDecken IX's wife as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better die while you're still \Nbeautiful and live in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess-sama!\N--How could you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't do that!\N--Run, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Yowahoshi! I told her to stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did Hordy-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading for the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! How dare \Nhe hurt Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go up there! You stay here \Nand take care of the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy, the ship is in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the ship is \Nfilled with water, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but I know Decken \Nis a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there must be air for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a coral that produces bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you to save \Nmy beloved Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to save Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi lures the Noah away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Luffy follows her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's cornered into an underwater battle \Nat a severe disadvantage against Hordy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Shirahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to finish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up, Luffy! Shirahoshi's \NLife in Jeopardy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
